  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Gathering chakra in your lungs and throat, you release a chilling roar that stumbles and frightens your enemies. All hostile creatures to you within a 120 ft. radius that can either see or hear you make a Wisdom saving throw. You may use Strength in place of Intelligence as your ninjutsu ability when casting this jutsu. A creature that fails this save gains three ranks of Fear for 1 minute, repeating the save at the end of each of its turns.</p><p>While a creature has these ranks of Fear and you are within line of sight, it cannot willingly move closer to you and cannot gain advantage by any effects. A creature that fails the initial save by 5 or more is Stunned until the end of its next turn. You gain 2 Temporary Hit Points and Chakra Points for every target that fails this saving throw as you feed on the fear surrounding you.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and the ranks of Fear inflicted by 1.</p>",
